    <p><strong>Date:</strong> ___ day of [Month], [Year]</p>

    <h3>Parties Involved</h3>

    <p><strong>Lender:</strong><br>
    Name: [Lender’s Full Name]<br>
    Address: [Lender’s Address]<br>
    Contact Information: [Phone Number, Email]</p>

    <p><strong>Borrower:</strong><br>
    Name: [Borrower’s Full Name]<br>
    Address: [Borrower’s Address]<br>
    Contact Information: [Phone Number, Email]</p>

    <h3>Recitals</h3>
    <p>The Lender agrees to provide the Borrower with a loan under the terms specified in this Agreement, and the Borrower agrees to repay the loan according to the repayment schedule. This Agreement includes provisions for asset seizure upon default.</p>

    <h3>1. Loan Terms</h3>

    <p class="section-title">1.1 Loan Amount:</p>
    <p>The Lender agrees to lend the Borrower the amount of <strong>$[Loan Amount]</strong> ("Loan Principal").</p>

    <p class="section-title">1.2 Interest Rate:</p>
    <p>The loan shall bear interest at a rate of <strong>[Interest Rate]% per annum</strong>, calculated from the date of disbursement until fully repaid.</p>

    <p class="section-title">1.3 Loan Disbursement Date:</p>
    <p>The loan will be disbursed on <strong>[Date of Loan Disbursement]</strong>.</p>

    <p class="section-title">1.4 Loan Term:</p>
    <p>The term of this loan is <strong>[Number] months/years</strong> from the date of disbursement.</p>

    <p class="section-title">1.5 Repayment Schedule:</p>
    <p>The Borrower agrees to repay the Loan Principal, plus interest, in <strong>[Number of Payments]</strong> equal installments of <strong>$[Amount per Installment]</strong>, due on the <strong>[day of the month]</strong> of each month, beginning on <strong>[First Payment Due Date]</strong> and ending on <strong>[Final Payment Due Date]</strong>.</p>

    <h3>2. Collateral and Asset Seizure</h3>

    <p class="section-title">2.1 Collateral Pledged:</p>
    <p>As security for the loan, the Borrower agrees to pledge the following assets ("Collateral") to the Lender:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Description of Asset 1: <strong>[Description of Collateral]</strong></li>
        <li>Description of Asset 2 (if applicable): <strong>[Description of Collateral]</strong></li>
    </ul>

    <p>The Borrower acknowledges that the Collateral will be used to secure the repayment of the loan. The Lender has the right to place a lien or any other security interest on the Collateral until the loan is fully repaid.</p>

    <p class="section-title">2.2 Rights Upon Default:</p>
    <p>If the Borrower defaults on the loan as described in Section 4 of this Agreement, the Lender has the legal right to seize and liquidate the Collateral to recover any outstanding amounts owed, including principal, interest, fees, and expenses.</p>

    <h3>3. Loan Repayment</h3>

    <p class="section-title">3.1 Payment Method:</p>
    <p>Payments shall be made via [Payment Method: check, bank transfer, etc.] to the following account or address:</p>
    <p><strong>Lender’s Bank Account:</strong><br>
    Bank Name: [Lender’s Bank]<br>
    Account Number: [Account Number]<br>
    Routing Number: [Routing Number]</p>

    <p class="section-title">3.2 Early Repayment:</p>
    <p>The Borrower may repay the loan in full at any time without penalty. Interest will be calculated only up to the date of full repayment.</p>

    <p class="section-title">3.3 Late Payment:</p>
    <p>In the event of late payment, the Borrower agrees to pay a late fee of <strong>$[Amount]</strong> for each day the payment is past due.</p>

    <h3>4. Default</h3>

    <p class="section-title">4.1 Events of Default:</p>
    <p>The Borrower shall be in default under this Agreement if any of the following occurs:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>
